Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this. It's a dollar. That's funny. Oh, no, sign the dollar, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:03:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign the dollar. Okay. And I know how much that's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for my question. Examination of something changes that which is examined. Calibrates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as a true statement. Yes. So my question is, when you're calibrating something, why does
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that not change what's being calibrated? I don't get the question. If I calibrate the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That doesn't change the energy field of the company. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you calibrate it a second time, it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it could vary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard calibrated at 200. It still calibrates at 200. It doesn't change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can prior prejudice affect the calibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on how expert you are at calibrating things. A very well-defined person can calibrate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing without intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, why would I want General Electric to calibrate higher or lower than it does? So
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the integrity of the question. The integrity of the question. If you want to know what
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing calibrates, that's one question. If you want to change it, that's something completely
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I have stock in General Electric, that won't change the calibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General Electric could be through the sky if that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody wants GE to go up because they bought the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Dr. Hawkins, do I have permission to shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. This is a question from my son who's in a mental hospital and he's taking meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a question of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From my son who's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in a mental hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's too close to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Can you hear me better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. This is from my son who's in a mental hospital and he's taking meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Abilify and Klonoprin. This is what he says. He's a student of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been using affirmations almost nonstop such as I love myself, Jesus heal me, Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,take these negative thoughts away. Now it is almost nine months later and I'm in a mental
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,hospital with uncontrollable shaking and anxiety. I am too afraid to continue the use of affirmations
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of what happened to me being in the hospital. Enlightenment seems out of the question and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I would simply like to have a nice, stable, happy life. How can I do this now that I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so out of it with the meds?
