Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about it for now. First, get your act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the answer. Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the road to enlightenment can take a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It can take a number of lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be just one step in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Try to get your life back together just on a normal level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry about enlightenment some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cats. You've got to be kidding.
