Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, do you have any tips for staying on the raiser's edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, intention plus endeavor will automatically handle it.
