Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly, look at all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't sign any of the Korean books, and that's what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question for you about a spiritual experience that I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a question about a spiritual experience that he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually explain it pretty well on page 220 of Eye of the Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, as the state of enlightenment presents itself, there's a glad moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as though experiencing a reentry into the profoundly familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fleeting transitory thought that one had forgotten who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This was forgetting was a consequence of the operation of perception itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing the Watching the Dots meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're having problems with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to speak directly to the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing the Watching the Dots meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it for about an hour and a half before I went to bed that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He took what an hour and a half before bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Watching the Fosgenous Meditation, where you close your eyes and you look at the dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you close your eyes and look at dots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And look what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You close your eyes and you see little dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I woke up and I was in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was all of a sudden everything melted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seemed like everything was melted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like perception, perceptual filter just dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was just like you say in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like reentry into the familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too long a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask, was this the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I experienced like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a fear of non-existence there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a fear of non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's like exactly how you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly how you explain it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like how I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not have come into existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ego's afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And where do I go with it from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This happened over a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wonders what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will I face this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know if it was the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that the void he experienced?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he get a glimpse at the void?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The void is nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So how...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's nothing, how could you get a glimpse of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a fear of non-existence there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a fear of non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a fear of non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to a certain level, you're afraid you're going to disappear and you will no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,longer exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your blessing, The devil no longer exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have your blessing and shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my book signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless your endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumping Jehoshaphat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to give you the wogglies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I often find it hard to differentiate when I'm coming from love or when it is from
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I remain pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I'm from love or from sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have difficulty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to understand, but when am I handling from sympathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has difficulty in knowing when he is coming from the sign of love
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it the sign of sympathy for that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know the difference between love and sympathy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion would answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion is better than sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sympathy is okay, but compassion is of a higher level of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, so compassion would be higher than sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than resonate at the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to sign this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They give me six books to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They want me to bless them and ask me a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And recite the Lord's Prayer backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,While standing on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going off to college next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to speak slower and more definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to college next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:14:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about the collaboration of the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of the universities in Sweden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the University of Sweden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the general in Sweden and in Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to know what the University of Sweden calibrates at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's where he's going to be attending school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,University of Sweden and Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 400, 450, 470, 460, 465, around 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And Stockholm, the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to calibrate Stockholm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants the calibration of Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stockholm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you asked me the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Stockholm is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care what Stockholm is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a big city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's where he's going to be living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stockholm calibrates over 300, 350, 340.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're on 340, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up Gabe while you're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabe is living in a small town in Sweden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he use the workforce?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long way to go for Swedish meatballs, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very nice to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was if you could explain some of the traps or pitfalls of the 400 level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectualism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectualism would be the obvious downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Intellectualism for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some guy on TV the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sort of a well-known personality, but I forget his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so smugly superior about how stupid it is to be a believer and how only an atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is intelligent, and he was so smug about it all, how stupid you are, could you believe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in God when there's no proof of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's a guy whose ego is all into his intellect, and he's dumber than hell, you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So stupid, he's pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:17:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to prove the existence of God with your intellect is, you know, for fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How to define the undefinable, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's a project.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was so smugly superior about it, I just thought, oh my God, this guy's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot realize the truth of God nor deny all of the truth of God through the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like sending a spade to do the job of a bulldozer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a professional atheist for years, so I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, the fire in the belly towards spiritual evolution seems to come in waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wonder if it, like, stabilizes or does it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he's having, you know, he has bits and glimpses and it comes like in waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's waves of spiritual…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…kind of comes over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says, does it stabilize or does it always kind of come up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For some, it stabilizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For others, it continues to come and go for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it reaches a profound level and then it stops fluctuating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So how would he, if he wants it to come in waves more, how would he just continue…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs to stop wanting it, wanting to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to surrender to God, then do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be telling God what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you shouldn't ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake your hand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God doesn't get offended by things that's comable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Either…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The book signed or do you want to shake my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With my feet, I could play you a tune on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It signs the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can whistle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I say names?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pay any attention to the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:20:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to say that I'm very thankful to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about a member of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought a picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Maria Claudia Rojas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was kidnapped about three years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in Colombia, South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to know if it's possible to know that if she
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is still alive or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She was abducted in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She was abducted or kidnapped in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if she's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why did you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she a relative or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was she on television, that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This picture was in a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask if this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I want to ask it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask, is this person still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not have permission to ask if this person is still
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,alive or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We sometimes get that with life and death and strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,or family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it isn't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's in the sign of hope, that you would give up hope
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if you knew she wasn't alive and that your prayers, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped the praying for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you can, put her on, her name on prayer groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I would do everything possible as far as it goes as, put her on every single prayer list
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been doing that since she got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, it's also you're dealing with karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what her karma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're dealing with both of those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's horrible not knowing what her karma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're dealing with both of those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's horrible not knowing what her karma is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a very good position to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, email us and we'll put her on our prayer list.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, we are from the Cape Town Study Group and we would like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They're from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cape Town Study Group in South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:22:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we would like to ask individually for your blessing and for your blessing on the study
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,group in Cape Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us to bless the study group in Cape Town, South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And they have, we have been sending them things for what, five years now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the study group has been in the, I mean, there for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:23:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey, you're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tweak your nose sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The illegible scrawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.31,0:24:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they want a blessing for South Africa, for their, uh …
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.40,0:24:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.89,0:24:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.89,0:24:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For their, uh, Cape, for the Cape Town studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we already have blessed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.22,0:24:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, did they what, bless us or?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.78,0:24:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think we can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.20,0:24:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.20,0:24:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we do send our blessing to that group in South Africa, and I think we have done
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.96,0:24:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so before, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.81,0:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wish it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.26,0:25:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting all of our books in foreign languages, a lot of people are here from foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.96,0:25:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,oh this is an interesting language it's called gobbledygook
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.20,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in gobbledygook yep
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they want to touch your hand over there oh thank you are they from south africa
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.88,0:25:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are you all from south africa okay
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.69,0:25:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,hello dr hawkins yes i first want to start by just saying thank you susan for your devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.19,0:26:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all these years i've got no questions i just want to say thank you doctor for your excellent sense
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of humor you just make it a pleasure to watch your work and get through it with with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.06,0:26:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the face there's my dollar for a blessing he wants a blessing and give you a dollar for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.13,0:26:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a blessing no no keep the dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,god bless you i don't charge a dollar anymore the irs wanted their cut of it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.76,0:26:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,i said it was god's money they said even god has to pay income tax no excuse boy oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.54,0:27:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's another question from the side okay my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.39,0:27:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is being a musician i study the works of mozart beethoven all these big musical giants but we all
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.86,0:27:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,know that when they were alive in their time they wasn't weren't appreciated by the society
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.99,0:27:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite the society thought mozart is a loser his music was never appreciated when he was alive
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.10,0:27:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is nowadays how we can determine is a good person is the truthful person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by just seeing his behavior like mozart or beethoven if you want to find beethoven you can
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,find under the bridge drum
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.47,0:27:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and always cross of people how good people make it short holy cats what is this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,history of mankind what is the question she says how do you determine if a person you know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.51,0:28:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like these uh artists were yeah yeah so how do you determine that if so is a good person
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.51,0:28:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's judgmental what do you mean by a good person i think uh drunken french artist is a fine
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.64,0:28:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,person to begin with very high well some of the artists are like this one that's a good person
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.55,0:28:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so, for instance, like, you know, these artists, a lot of them had other problems, like alcoholism and that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.22,0:28:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you determine that, you know, any...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.57,0:28:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't ask the question. What do you mean by a good person? According to what definition and what is a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.44,0:28:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Like the music of Mozart calibrates above 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.64,0:28:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.72,0:28:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mozart calibrates about 500. So how do you determine...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.57,0:28:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask the arm. Mozart's level of consciousness is, and then I find out what it is. Yeah. He also had extremely high IQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:29:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Through kinesiology or muscle testing, you could find out whether this person, what their intentions were and whether or not they would be a good person, as you put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily looking at the actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.18,0:29:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing being a great artist, another being a good person. You can be a great artist and be an SOB, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.26,0:29:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's two different...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.25,0:29:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be a saint, but a lousy artist. The world's full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.56,0:29:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.43,0:29:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also from South Africa. It was in our little present with cards, and we want these cards to be signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.75,0:29:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so poor when I was young, I couldn't afford to be an artist. I couldn't afford the paints. I couldn't afford the canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.14,0:29:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up being an artist. The pigments were expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.43,0:30:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were a member of the Art Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.61,0:30:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Art Institute. Yeah, I used to pose for them. They'd give me $10 an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.19,0:30:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth. I couldn't afford it, but I could make 10 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.80,0:30:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They allowed me to drape my pants over certain areas of my life for 10 bucks. Otherwise, I wanted 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.45,0:30:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.36,0:30:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,David, you're not supposed to be telling me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.98,0:30:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,10 bucks will do, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.17,0:30:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to be telling me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.17,0:30:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was. I was wandering. I was in the Navy, wandering through the San Francisco Art Institute, and this lady came over to me and asked me, did I want to pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:31:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They needed a young male model. I was in the Navy. 10 bucks an hour sounded like good money to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.05,0:31:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the story in my head. That's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.15,0:31:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Made quick 10 bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.46,0:31:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Hi, Dr. Hawkins. I don't have a question. I just wanted to say thank you and tell you that you mean so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.46,0:31:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Hi, Dr. Hawkins. I just wanted to say thank you and tell you that you mean so much to me.
