Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.15,0:39:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Like throwing up, fainting,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.76,0:39:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,passing out, getting angry, getting
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.55,0:39:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,goosebumps? No, like
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.26,0:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,insomnia, and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.84,0:39:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,um,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.98,0:39:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,my fingers turn white,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.13,0:39:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.46,0:39:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the heart. Yeah, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.61,0:39:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I have nothing to be upset
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.76,0:39:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about. I have a great life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.65,0:39:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't figure out why
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.69,0:39:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,my body
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.76,0:39:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.44,0:39:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.53,0:39:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,psychiatric problem. Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.78,0:39:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.51,0:39:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you very much. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.00,0:39:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.69,0:39:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.78,0:39:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we're trying to do three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.76,0:39:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.05,0:39:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.80,0:40:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.36,0:40:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste. First of all, I want
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.57,0:40:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to thank you, and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.67,0:40:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your presence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.78,0:40:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I only want to ask for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.69,0:40:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,your blessings, so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.82,0:40:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.67,0:40:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,have more success with my healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.96,0:40:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,um, it's a holistic healing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.67,0:40:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,practice, and help
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.94,0:40:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,more people. She wants what? Blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.01,0:40:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a blessing on her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.13,0:40:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic healing practice, so that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.76,0:40:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,she can help more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.69,0:40:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sure, I bless your
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,holistic healing. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.71,0:40:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yep. Can I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.98,0:40:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.15,0:40:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.90,0:41:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.59,0:41:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We came together, we are friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.94,0:41:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and we would like
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.46,0:41:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to just receive a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,trial, a silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.63,0:41:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.80,0:41:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They just want to feel your silence
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.73,0:41:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,transmission. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.42,0:41:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So, put it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.01,0:41:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.11,0:41:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you both, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.32,0:41:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you both. God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.19,0:41:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Oh, good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.07,0:42:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.36,0:42:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.59,0:42:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.90,0:42:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, how can I heal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.48,0:42:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,inner judgmentalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.48,0:42:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How can I heal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.17,0:42:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,judgmentalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.34,0:42:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I heal inner judgmentalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.53,0:42:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you heal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.61,0:42:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,interjudgmentalism?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.28,0:42:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Being self-critical. Stop doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.36,0:42:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you stop picking your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.21,0:42:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pick it. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.80,0:42:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that. Well, do you know when you're doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.61,0:42:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I know when I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.15,0:42:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well then... Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you know when you're doing it, then stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.82,0:43:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the radio. Watch television.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.17,0:43:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.13,0:43:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go meditate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.09,0:43:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're qualified to judge
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.25,0:43:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,people that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.01,0:43:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or judge?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.34,0:43:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're qualified to judge things that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.73,0:43:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.80,0:43:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pray instead. Pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.84,0:43:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask God to remove these defects of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.01,0:43:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.03,0:43:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.92,0:43:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.46,0:43:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.76,0:43:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't want to shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.46,0:43:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask God to remove your defects of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.65,0:43:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Live one day at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it simple. Easy does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.96,0:43:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.55,0:43:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get with the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.03,0:44:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.69,0:44:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask you if I could sit next to you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.78,0:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for a couple of questions for the silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.46,0:44:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.96,0:44:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to sit next to you for a couple of questions
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.21,0:44:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for the silent transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.65,0:44:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't have to sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.34,0:44:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask me what you want to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.13,0:44:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.15,0:44:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working with shame at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.92,0:44:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I would like to ask you if you have any pointers
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.19,0:44:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,how to heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.32,0:44:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's working with shame at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.26,0:44:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.76,0:44:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you give him some pointers?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.23,0:44:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you give him some pointers as to how to overcome that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.05,0:44:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame, ah, look at it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.92,0:44:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame is egocentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.46,0:44:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh me, how bad I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.55,0:44:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh me, oh me, oh me, oh me, oh me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.82,0:45:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I do that, oh me?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.55,0:45:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up being egocentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.90,0:45:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to judge yourself is egocentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.32,0:45:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I good, am I bad, or was I terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.84,0:45:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, give up egocentricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.71,0:45:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop looking in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.71,0:45:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look in the mirror at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.55,0:45:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry about other people who need your help
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.61,0:45:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.46,0:45:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.40,0:45:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.69,0:45:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You get over shame through forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.59,0:45:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.21,0:45:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have a weak human ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.59,0:45:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were born human.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.98,0:45:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born human, you have an ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.03,0:45:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego's only concerned with me, me, me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.00,0:45:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.67,0:45:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.63,0:45:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.19,0:45:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm. Jacob here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.03,0:45:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come from Coventry. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.63,0:46:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Coventry, England, say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.53,0:46:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.15,0:46:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coventry, England.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.71,0:46:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,England.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.82,0:46:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coventry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.63,0:46:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coventry, England.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.30,0:46:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.01,0:46:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And haven't got a question really.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.76,0:46:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like to shake your hand, me and Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.36,0:46:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come right on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.30,0:46:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.07,0:46:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.75,0:46:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since we've been in London, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.63,0:46:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.92,0:46:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.71,0:46:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want to tell you, I thank God every day that I found your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.84,0:46:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank God now that I found, I finally had a chance to see you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.80,0:47:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.46,0:47:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand a word she's mumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.38,0:47:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.67,0:47:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.19,0:47:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.46,0:47:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.40,0:47:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.75,0:47:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop mumbling and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.69,0:47:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not really crying, it's kind of like.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.76,0:47:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.78,0:47:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, oh my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.26,0:47:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be an extra dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.26,0:47:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over, baby, give me the nice keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.80,0:47:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.86,0:47:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the nice keys right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.36,0:47:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All the women want your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.69,0:47:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All the women are fighting after my little body.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.96,0:47:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, narcissism.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.34,0:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.11,0:48:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins and Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.98,0:48:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, I want to thank you both for doing all the work that you do for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.59,0:48:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.88,0:48:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.80,0:48:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have one question, and I have a blessing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.23,0:48:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people I respect think that promoting divine and unconditional love to everything in the universe is the proper path, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.80,0:48:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what he said, he's reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.57,0:48:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.57,0:48:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to write this down because it's a heavy question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.13,0:48:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.63,0:48:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.63,0:48:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.36,0:48:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get right to the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.86,0:48:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have it both ways and have a wonderful, loving relationship while devoting our lives to service unto God?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.94,0:48:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.94,0:48:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have it both ways and have a wonderful, loving relationship while devoting our lives to service unto others?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.94,0:48:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do both?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.19,0:48:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we be in love with one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.26,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.26,0:48:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And still have enough to give to the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.26,0:48:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.26,0:48:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.26,0:48:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.55,0:48:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting you to answer like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.55,0:48:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So finally, my blessing is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.55,0:48:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I please ask that you, Dr. Hawkins, and the audience, give a blessing to my soon-to-be-asked
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.32,0:49:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,fiancée, Tiffany, and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.01,0:49:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.01,0:49:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the whole audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.01,0:49:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.01,0:49:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to do that spiritual prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.36,0:49:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.36,0:49:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.36,0:49:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.36,0:49:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.36,0:49:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.36,0:49:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.36,0:49:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.36,0:49:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.36,0:49:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.36,0:49:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.36,0:49:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.07,0:49:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.07,0:49:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tine, you have the honor to introduce me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.94,0:49:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Masa Mr. Ballasoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.98,0:49:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say that a little bit louder?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.48,0:49:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the name of the band, Missantia?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.48,0:49:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's the name of the band, Missantia?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.84,0:49:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please,最 Nations Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.84,0:49:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.84,0:49:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.84,0:50:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to hear you out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.23,0:50:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you about what Young Lotney did?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.23,0:50:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.23,0:50:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sent you best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.23,0:50:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say that a little bit louder?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.23,0:50:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let those who can hear, hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.30,0:50:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let those who can see, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.30,0:50:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we certainly send you the best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.46,0:50:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We send you the best wishes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.46,0:50:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.92,0:50:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.92,0:50:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Little ones but lots and lots of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.92,0:50:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a big one, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.92,0:50:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.32,0:50:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.32,0:50:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.73,0:50:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.73,0:50:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.98,0:50:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think, when I go home on my drive back to Toronto, we should drive four hours out
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.42,0:50:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of our way to see the Grand Canyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.28,0:50:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No calibration necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.03,0:50:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.03,0:50:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go and see Niagara Falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.82,0:50:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.82,0:50:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.07,0:50:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.07,0:50:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Niagara Falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.07,0:50:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.07,0:50:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.07,0:51:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you better see the Grand Canyon, because it might be gone by the time you get
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.38,0:51:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.38,0:51:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.38,0:51:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.38,0:51:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.59,0:51:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.59,0:51:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.67,0:51:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the President went to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.67,0:51:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the President go and see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.36,0:51:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.36,0:51:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The President was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.36,0:51:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.36,0:51:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.36,0:51:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.05,0:51:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.59,0:51:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.59,0:51:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to sit here and look into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.40,0:51:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your work and your autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I started reading your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.61,0:51:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been April, and it's been wonderful for me, and I'm sure many other people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.80,0:51:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.82,0:51:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The bagpiper at the beginning, I was crying through the whole thing, and I've never done
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.11,0:51:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that before with bagpipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.11,0:51:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.96,0:52:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he cried through the whole bagpipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.98,0:52:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's the first time I've ever cried at bagpipes, usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.84,0:52:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I cry because they go on too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.84,0:52:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.84,0:52:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that really have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.90,0:52:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.26,0:52:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.26,0:52:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a set of bagpipes at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.26,0:52:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're hanging on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.26,0:52:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.26,0:52:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.26,0:52:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.50,0:52:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would also like to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.50,0:52:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.50,0:52:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.50,0:52:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the pipes are on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.50,0:52:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.55,0:52:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.88,0:52:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One is, what does the big book of Alcoholics Anonymous calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.88,0:52:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.88,0:52:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.26,0:52:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.26,0:52:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done it before, but I don't remember what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.26,0:52:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.26,0:52:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is called The Big Book of Alcoholics Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.26,0:52:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book about alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.26,0:52:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book about alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.26,0:52:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book about alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.26,0:52:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book about alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.26,0:52:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a book about alcoholics.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.00,0:53:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is over 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.00,0:53:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The book is over 700, 750, 725, 730.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.76,0:53:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,720 is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.76,0:53:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my other question is, you know, I'm coming up on 20 years in the program, and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.96,0:53:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in the last year-
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.21,0:53:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.21,0:53:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in the program 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.21,0:53:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.21,0:53:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to stop drinking, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.21,0:53:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.21,0:53:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, in the last year, when I finally found out that I was going to be an alcoholic,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.21,0:53:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.21,0:53:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.21,0:53:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.21,0:53:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.21,0:53:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.21,0:53:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.86,0:53:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.86,0:53:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.86,0:53:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.86,0:53:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.86,0:53:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.21,0:53:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.48,0:53:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.48,0:53:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.48,0:53:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, in the last year, when I find myself meditating or feeling that gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.19,0:53:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for God's grace, I find myself just starting to just weep uncontrollably, and I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.78,0:53:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.78,0:53:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good, but it's- I just don't understand it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.34,0:53:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, understand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.13,0:53:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to mentalize about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.82,0:53:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.82,0:53:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I-
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.82,0:54:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.82,0:54:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.98,0:54:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.30,0:54:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.30,0:54:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.30,0:54:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them how many years you have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.05,0:54:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.05,0:54:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.38,0:54:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,47.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.38,0:54:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew Bill Wilson, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.38,0:54:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.38,0:54:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.38,0:54:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.38,0:54:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to speak together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.61,0:54:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to speak together at the- there was a retreat house for alcoholic priests in Michigan,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.05,0:54:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and Bill and I used to speak there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.34,0:54:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.86,0:54:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.86,0:54:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.86,0:54:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from the Edmonton group, up in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.21,0:54:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.21,0:54:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And we got a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.21,0:54:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We went down to a park two blocks away from my friend Pat's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.01,0:54:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It says Hawkins Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.01,0:55:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's got Edmonton on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.01,0:55:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.01,0:55:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.01,0:55:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy by the name of Ken holding a cat, and I got a coffee, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.01,0:55:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.01,0:55:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just need cigarettes in there, and I think it'll be all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.01,0:55:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Save that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.01,0:55:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.51,0:55:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also recently started an electrical company, and I named it Integrity Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.51,0:55:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was inspired by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.51,0:55:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.51,0:55:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems to be going very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.51,0:55:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the doors are opening wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.51,0:55:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a company?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.51,0:55:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Electrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.51,0:55:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, uh, doing electrical work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.51,0:55:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Electrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.69,0:55:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.69,0:55:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Running wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.69,0:55:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.69,0:55:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.69,0:55:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I like electrical work.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.69,0:55:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shocking, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.69,0:55:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.69,0:55:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of current.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.73,0:55:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're well grounded, you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.73,0:55:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay if we took a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.78,0:55:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.78,0:55:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.78,0:55:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.78,0:55:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.78,0:55:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.57,0:55:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.57,0:55:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.09,0:55:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.09,0:55:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.09,0:55:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.09,0:55:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.09,0:55:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.09,0:55:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.09,0:55:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.09,0:56:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.46,0:56:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.46,0:56:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.46,0:56:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.55,0:56:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.69,0:56:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't brand it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.69,0:56:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.30,0:56:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.86,0:56:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a chance to get a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.46,0:56:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.46,0:56:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have his?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.46,0:56:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.46,0:56:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okie doke.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.38,0:56:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.38,0:56:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okie doke.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.38,0:56:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.38,0:56:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.38,0:56:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.38,0:56:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.38,0:56:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.38,0:56:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.73,0:56:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mrs. Hawkins.
