Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.06,1:10:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you know like creating a boundary between yourself and someone like you said don't spend too much
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.56,1:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,time with your family members who are rude to you that's part of it it's not necessarily hugging
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.05,1:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody and saying oh you're so lovely and i like your shirt and what is she asking what is
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.93,1:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she asking i don't want the recitation all right sorry no that's all right i was busy doing
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.73,1:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,something um okay she wants to know how
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.00,1:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you go about showing that love for someone i can't explain it to you it's automatic when you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.52,1:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,love somebody it's automatic there isn't any kind of a thing you can memorize what to do
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.55,1:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so if you love a puppy you love the puppy if it cries you you feed it you love it i don't
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.27,1:11:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,explain what she means were you never on planet earth as a human what is your question well she
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.89,1:11:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to know how do you show love i mean how do you don't you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.05,1:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,go to the movies don't you have relatives don't you have friends you go to school i don't go to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.98,1:11:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,school yeah i have friends i have family huh she has friends and family yes yes so you know what
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.13,1:11:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is it like yes uh-huh and that's all things so what is the question please i should have thought
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.02,1:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about this more um there we go so so anyway she what it is is basically does she uh
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.23,1:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,watch what she's thinking and she's also thinking of her family okay she even likes her family
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.88,1:12:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,man okay great audience she wants her family to accompany them so that way she doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.92,1:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be a different DJ that's cool whatever you do but she's enjoying the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.92,1:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,community she's enjoying the new time she's enjoying the new place she's enjoying the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.50,1:12:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,life it's so wonderful and so fascinating for me what was one thing that you used for
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.46,1:12:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or what did you use to do to make your family like or even you know what did you do as a
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.23,1:12:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,person
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.57,1:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they scare you, and you don't want to be around them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.64,1:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk away from them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.69,1:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, you can still pray for them that they will change.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.80,1:12:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still pray.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.69,1:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that, you know, they do not hurt you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.85,1:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not necessarily hugging them and kissing them and being their best friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.07,1:12:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not physically.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.10,1:12:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's say a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.78,1:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold them in mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.89,1:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.64,1:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.48,1:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.89,1:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.19,1:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.31,1:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry that I'm too harsh with people.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.30,1:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I can be very, like, get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.85,1:13:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm like, is that very loving?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.56,1:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you say a prayer?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.43,1:13:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.93,1:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.72,1:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is not just black and white.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.61,1:13:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's various shades of gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.57,1:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is various shades of gray.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.96,1:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Very seldom is it just black or just white.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.23,1:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.47,1:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It subtly moves from one little thing to another,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.38,1:13:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like the breeze through the leaves in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.07,1:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we shake your hand?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.26,1:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.68,1:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cheesy now.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.68,1:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.13,1:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I'll have a...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.81,1:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.23,1:13:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.73,1:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.92,1:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.89,1:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.01,1:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for your work and your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.86,1:13:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been very helpful to me in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.47,1:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to know if I could receive your blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.18,1:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.39,1:14:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.10,1:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it's useful to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.85,1:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Essentially, I'm a pragmatist.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.56,1:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.89,1:14:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.06,1:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you for your teachings.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.02,1:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything you've done for my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.61,1:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask if I could shake your hand and have your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.84,1:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know if I can walk and chew gum at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.35,1:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.72,1:14:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.56,1:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can walk and chew gum at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.93,1:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.53,1:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By divine dispensation.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.46,1:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.96,1:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.36,1:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.84,1:15:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.22,1:15:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wanted to get to know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.69,1:15:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to come and say thank you to you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.42,1:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I made you a present.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.47,1:15:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.27,1:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.10,1:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,keep track of who gets this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.39,1:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.43,1:15:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,say thank you and how much we enjoy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.26,1:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,studying your work.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.47,1:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.72,1:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.69,1:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed so many people's lives
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.65,1:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody is so grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.10,1:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hopefully. Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.27,1:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.76,1:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And we wanted to have a picture taken with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.98,1:16:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They want a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.10,1:16:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.31,1:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.26,1:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.19,1:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.60,1:16:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.26,1:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you pay
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.92,1:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to see the pyramids?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.53,1:16:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You said $10?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.85,1:16:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no fee.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.42,1:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's allowed to go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.14,1:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They have guards.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.73,1:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he wants to know about the experience
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.76,1:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that you, when you were meditating
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.46,1:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pyramids, what was the experience?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.65,1:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot describe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.85,1:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was transcendental.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.10,1:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was transcendental.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.90,1:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.92,1:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To be alone all night
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.07,1:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the great pyramids
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.30,1:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be described.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.57,1:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be experienced, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.40,1:17:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.65,1:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the whole pyramid to myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.50,1:17:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.35,1:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you go into a high state
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.03,1:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when you were in the pyramids?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.89,1:17:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.48,1:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it like, you know, some of the states
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.86,1:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that I have seen you in?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.71,1:18:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say it was transcendental.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.17,1:18:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost all reference points.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.81,1:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.10,1:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.56,1:18:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.52,1:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Between you and the sky,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.84,1:18:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there's 400 feet of stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.10,1:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silent beyond all capacity for silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.43,1:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And there were other entities
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.89,1:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.27,1:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imagine the pyramid attracts
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.11,1:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,too many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.93,1:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imagine this amount of spiritual interest
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.03,1:18:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from huge numbers of people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.10,1:18:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for many decades.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.61,1:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.60,1:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it would be like a spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.31,1:18:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whose job it is to come to people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.64,1:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who meditate,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.89,1:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to come to you for like reassurance
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.15,1:19:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that your intention
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.81,1:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is known
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.50,1:19:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,by your trip
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.90,1:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from around the world
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.27,1:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to just be here
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.25,1:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,alone with God all night long
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.42,1:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the complete total silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.48,1:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very different kind of experience
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.42,1:19:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,than you can really explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.72,1:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes being in one of the great cathedrals
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.86,1:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that we've been in,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.85,1:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole cathedral is completely deserted.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.90,1:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single person.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.18,1:19:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got a whole cathedral all to ourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.64,1:19:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that's happened to us several times.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.18,1:19:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to describe.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.72,1:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant silent cathedral
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.00,1:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're the only ones there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.13,1:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just you and the cathedral
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.14,1:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the stained glass window.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.13,1:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannot be described.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.25,1:19:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's experiential and transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.85,1:19:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcendent is about the only term I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.42,1:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when you walk the,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.42,1:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what, the maze.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.42,1:20:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.00,1:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You walk the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.11,1:20:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.64,1:20:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be described.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.14,1:20:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.97,1:20:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.31,1:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.89,1:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,would it be helpful to cancel the belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.05,1:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's more difficult for a,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.56,1:20:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for a female body to reach,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.25,1:20:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to survive the higher levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.44,1:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,than a male body?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.90,1:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we survive birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.92,1:20:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.22,1:20:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.88,1:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, she wants to,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.42,1:20:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,she said, would it be good to cancel the belief system
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.03,1:20:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's easier for a male body
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.27,1:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach enlightenment than a female body?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.42,1:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who holds that belief system?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.50,1:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that the reason that there's less, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.18,1:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that the reason that there's less, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.26,1:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you say that the reason that there's less,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.35,1:21:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,women at the higher levels of consciousness on your charts
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.15,1:21:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is because the female body can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.89,1:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be, yeah, the female physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.93,1:21:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.47,1:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier for the male body to handle the stress
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.68,1:21:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of a high-level consciousness to resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.06,1:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.14,1:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any limitation involved in the belief of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.43,1:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.27,1:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any limitation involved in the belief?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.39,1:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a fact, you know, it's just a fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.72,1:21:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you plan to get enlightened in this lifetime, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.57,1:21:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to realize my fullest potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.60,1:21:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.35,1:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.38,1:21:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.84,1:21:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.06,1:21:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,May I shake your hand, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.97,1:21:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete your highest completeness.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.26,1:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you reach a certain stage, and you drop dead,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.52,1:21:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you get reborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.89,1:21:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what it's all about?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.26,1:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.19,1:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like electrical, you know, like you're being electrified,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.28,1:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, within your skin when you hit certain levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.09,1:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And so it's, you know, it's just not pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.51,1:22:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.98,1:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take separate study about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.89,1:22:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's something I ran across over the years,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.76,1:22:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never set out a study plan about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.15,1:22:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. We're going to do a little bit something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.11,1:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all of our staff members, if they would come up on stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.00,1:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to give them a hand for this year of helping us
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.60,1:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of the lectures, and if all of you could come upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.00,1:22:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have about 20 people that help put
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.80,1:22:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on these lectures, including people that handle the parking and all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.46,1:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm going to go down the line here and ask for them to give us their names.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.39,1:23:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you could, and maybe you all could tell what you do for Veritas.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.67,1:23:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.05,1:23:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gabriel, I do production.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.68,1:23:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, who are all these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.06,1:23:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ethel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.77,1:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I do that arm banding.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.07,1:23:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them look strangely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.22,1:23:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.50,1:23:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.61,1:23:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in the office.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.51,1:23:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura, I work in the office.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.36,1:23:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Donna, I work in the bookstore and production.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.14,1:23:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Darlene Greeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.47,1:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeremy in the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.52,1:23:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Julie, production.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.57,1:23:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Vicki, bookstore and production.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.52,1:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna, bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.22,1:23:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lynn, bookstore, production.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.56,1:23:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack, bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.82,1:23:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gisela, office and registration.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.39,1:23:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don, bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.86,1:23:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's our healer, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.68,1:23:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He does work on everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.81,1:23:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don, guard at the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.56,1:23:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Janice.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.56,1:23:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the PowerPoint.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.56,1:23:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Wally.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.56,1:23:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.56,1:23:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lonnie, and I stand at the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.56,1:23:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Demet, and I do what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.56,1:23:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm George.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.56,1:23:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I work up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.56,1:23:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Cynthia.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.56,1:23:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I work back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.64,1:23:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.64,1:24:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I help with the parking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.64,1:24:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.72,1:24:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I get stuck with the parking too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.72,1:24:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.72,1:24:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.96,1:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.96,1:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.96,1:24:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.96,1:24:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.96,1:24:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.96,1:24:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.96,1:24:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.96,1:24:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.96,1:24:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.96,1:24:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm John.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.47,1:24:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.47,1:24:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Brian.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.96,1:24:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I do parking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.96,1:24:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Steve, wherever needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.85,1:24:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's others that are in the bookstore that aren't even here, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.55,1:24:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, north.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.55,1:24:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.10,1:24:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Scott.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.10,1:24:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I work in production and parking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.10,1:24:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, and parking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.38,1:24:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison, mostly bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.01,1:24:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathy, bookstore, and walk-ins.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.05,1:24:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Josh, production.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.40,1:24:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's a couple more that are in bookstore that aren't out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.51,1:24:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lisa?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.51,1:24:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Lisa and John that work here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.51,1:24:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that are their trailhead.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.64,1:24:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They do all of our production.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.10,1:24:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.92,1:25:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's John? Back there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.68,1:25:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fran?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.50,1:25:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fran?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.85,1:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Photographer, Fran.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.00,1:25:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fran?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.19,1:25:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these people have full-time jobs
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.10,1:25:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then come out and help us out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.19,1:25:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In so many ways, I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.89,1:25:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're so appreciative that we have a staff
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.02,1:25:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that takes such good care of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.27,1:25:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And if all of you could give them a big hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.80,1:25:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,we would appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.86,1:25:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.18,1:25:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.10,1:25:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.50,1:25:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.94,1:25:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.56,1:25:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly, there's that many people.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.84,1:25:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you got now?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.64,1:25:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to come up here and say goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.22,1:26:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to let the staff stay up here, if you would,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.61,1:26:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because you need to feel this energy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.85,1:26:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes off this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.72,1:26:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we doing, honey?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.10,1:26:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am all by myself out in the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.31,1:26:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.89,1:26:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.64,1:26:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello? Smile?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.80,1:26:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we could do the music.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.11,1:26:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you could say a few words
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.30,1:26:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll do some music.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.92,1:26:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.03,1:26:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.77,1:26:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the music?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.10,1:26:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.47,1:26:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.22,1:26:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.36,1:26:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.67,1:27:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God wrote that song.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.40,1:27:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It represents an aspect of God
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.55,1:27:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that cannot be verbalized
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.75,1:27:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond intellection.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.63,1:27:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming off the coast,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.22,1:27:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the Pacific coast in California one time,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.31,1:27:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up above,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.68,1:27:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and here were these giant, these huge birds,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.46,1:27:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wind was coming off the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.27,1:27:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way the birds maintained themselves there,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.23,1:27:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they did not flap their wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.68,1:27:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These giant birds were just angled themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.97,1:27:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.39,1:28:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like so, and like so, and like so, and like so.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.42,1:28:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds just made the most minute movements,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.06,1:28:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and instead it took advantage of the power of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.06,1:28:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So with practically no expenditure of energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.51,1:28:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the birds stayed up there for like half an hour,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.36,1:28:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,an hour at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.56,1:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All they did was move their little bodies a slight half
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.56,1:28:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,an inch this way, and this wing would go up half an inch
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.88,1:28:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.06,1:28:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.61,1:28:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To be with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.81,1:28:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You angle yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.30,1:28:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the energy of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.89,1:28:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,flows through you,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.92,1:28:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the angle of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.11,1:29:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it uplifts you and sustains you
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.61,1:29:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,through a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.97,1:29:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The winds of God sustain us.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.89,1:29:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank the Lord for this life,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.34,1:29:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for the beauty of this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.38,1:29:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The real power of beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.67,1:29:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-verbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.80,1:30:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you hear this particular music,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.31,1:30:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're instantly in a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.06,1:30:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What it expresses is grace,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.13,1:30:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the grace of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.43,1:30:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of God's grace
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.60,1:30:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is the awareness of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.27,1:30:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who do not walk in God's grace
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.38,1:30:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,are oblivious to beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.59,1:30:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,oblivious to kindness.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.42,1:30:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's love at the highest level.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.97,1:30:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a name, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.42,1:30:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Agape is that,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.39,1:31:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and so transcends personal love, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.85,1:31:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you cannot reach God
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.85,1:31:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,by bypassing love.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.93,1:31:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A bird cannot get all the way up
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.93,1:31:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to a higher elevation
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.50,1:31:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without going through these various layers.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.50,1:31:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So we position ourself
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.77,1:31:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in a loving way.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.57,1:31:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We say, thank you, God,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.05,1:31:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the blessings of this life,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.93,1:31:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for the chance to experience each other
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.93,1:31:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,at a meeting like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.65,1:31:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions and millions of people,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.72,1:31:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions and millions of people,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.73,1:31:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,millions and millions of people,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.73,1:31:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,millions and millions of people,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.84,1:31:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,live and die
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.34,1:31:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and never have a single experience
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.68,1:31:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,like the people in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.84,1:31:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,around here right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.64,1:31:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions live and die
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.72,1:31:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,bereft of any spiritual experience
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.39,1:31:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or awareness or opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.94,1:32:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it takes many lifetimes to earn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.22,1:32:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.60,1:32:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes many lifetimes to earn to be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.43,1:32:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.85,1:32:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thank our own past selves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.02,1:32:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you get fragments of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.17,1:32:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that there were moments
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.67,1:32:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,of great contrition for having made mistakes
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.97,1:32:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then bring to God in a very intense earnestness
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.96,1:32:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which God responded by allowing us
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.38,1:33:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to come into this lifetime to fulfill that desire.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.42,1:33:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So we thank thee, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.07,1:33:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for the gift of all these people present,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.23,1:33:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,all aligned with reaching God in divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.19,1:33:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all aligned with reaching God in divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.69,1:33:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,relying upon the love of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.34,1:33:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The bagpipes have a certain energy that's specific,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.30,1:33:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and this particular music has an energy
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.85,1:34:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that is specific to this style of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.17,1:34:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One's not better than the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.11,1:34:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just different aspects.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.15,1:34:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank thee, oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.11,1:34:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for the blessing of this group of people here assembled,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.69,1:34:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we pray for those who are missing today
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.26,1:34:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,because of illness.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.47,1:34:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.31,1:35:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is joy indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.00,1:35:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can handle, my nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.84,1:35:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.84,1:35:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.81,1:35:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.13,1:35:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.02,1:35:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
